{"tid":1767931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［警世］見到熱門啲post覺得好嬲嘅人入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-12-03T16:18:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-03T16:32:28.000Z","uid":133466,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"142df20581b686e11c2a9c03688dee1c43791be2","tid":1767931,"uid":133466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T16:18:11.000Z","msg":"我明<br />\n我明你見到熱門呢堆垃圾post一定嬲到震㗎啦<br />\n心諗你班廢柴 行動post又唔推 喺度傾埋啲戇鳩野<br />\n但係我好想同你講<br />\n依家真係冇人從連燈睇熱門<br />\n抗爭從來都係要自己主動去做<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">如果一個活動係因為連登唔推post而冇人去<br />\n咁唔該你班仆街自己諗清楚點解啲義士要為你地犧牲<br />\n你哋每講一句廢話每推一個廢post嘅時候<br />\n大撚把義士受緊折磨</span></strong></span><br />\n但真心嘅 如果你見到呢班熱門嘅仆街唔順氣<br />\n你咪落街痴文宣囉<br />\n講咗幾撚多次<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><ins>癡一張文宣派一張傳單有用過你喺連登推10次post</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n所以真心嘅 如果你覺得嬲<br />\n直接放棄連登啦 我啲friend依家都唔上㗎啦<br />\n大家睇活動都係睇tg <br />\n落街痴文宣啦 推唔起啲post就放棄啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利伸呢個唔係文宣post 但循例都宣傳下啦<br />\n都成半年啦 大家醒小小 <br />\n自己主動去搵有乜嘢活動可以參加<br />\n而唔係要人哋同你講啦 唔該<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uuj94Au.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fuuj94Au.jpg&h=41aafd65&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Js4ewfx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJs4ewfx.png&h=ce665a0d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rCMXt2c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrCMXt2c.jpg&h=9348dec4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xmwXt2d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxmwXt2d.jpg&h=fc3c9466&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"49023c775a151c20187947a44e7fbb399ddf7927","tid":1767931,"uid":133466,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T16:19:37.000Z","msg":"cap呢個post比你身邊啲朋友睇<br />\n全民落街癡文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma